Package com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.task

Class TasksPageDto

java.lang.Object
com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.task.TasksPageDto
public class TasksPageDto extends Object
Data Transfer Object for representing a page of tasks within a project. This class encapsulates details about the project's name, a specific project task, a list of tasks, the type of user viewing the tasks, project members, project progress, and the project's state.
